  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Inghams was founded by Walter Ingham in 1934 and specialises in ski holidays, walking holidays and holidays to Lapland. Walter was passionate about sharing all that our amazing planet has to offer with others from around Britain, be it cruising down a slope on skis, chasing the Northern lights on a sleigh or walking to the best view points across Europe. We aim to carry on that sense of adventure in all our holidays to this day.</p>
<p>If you're looking for a career that's not just a job but a fulfilling adventure, we welcome you to explore opportunities with us. Join our team and be part of a dynamic, purpose-driven business dedicated to making a positive impact in the world.</p>
<h3>Inghams UK Head Office Job Opportunities</h3>
<p>In our UK head office based in Farnborough, Hampshire, we're regularly recruiting for roles across all areas of the business, from sales and administration, to product and marketing and many more. Find out what it's like to work at Inghams and view all the opportunities currently available on our UK careers site. </p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://careers.inghams.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Hotelplan UK Careers" class="c-btn">View all UK Head Office job opportunities</a></p>
<h3>Inghams Overseas Roles</h3>
<p>Our largest body of seasonal staff is overseas. In summer and winter, we recruit resort managers, resort administrators and representatives into overseas jobs. In our winter chalet resorts, we recruit chalet and hotel staff and management.</p>
<p>Inghams has a number of seasonal vacancies available for the forthcoming winter season.</p>
<p>For vacancies overseas, please visit our in-house recruitment website <a rel="noopener" href="http://www.workaseason.com/" target="_blank">www.workaseason.com</a>, to view a full list of the available positions and how to apply.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://careers.workaseason.com/" target="_blank" title="Workaseasons" class="c-btn">Visit Workaseason</a></p>
<p><a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://media/203fbe362a934d6c8e755c74d85fa57a" href="/media/13067887/privacy-statement.pdf" target="_blank" title="Employee Privacy Statement.pdf"><em>Employee Privacy Statement</em></a></p>]]></bodyText>
